---
title: Pan Fried Duck with Spring Onion Mash, Roasted Bok and Plum Hoisin Sauce
description: We love good Duck with Greens, Potatoes and Plum Sauce and this deliciously simple, chef-curated recipe doesn't disappoint. Time to bust out the pots and pans!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5eb43ce72e969f3d544bb4cf-ce76c4f8-71a6bc60.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/pan-fried-duck-5eb43ce72e969f3d544bb4cf-a0a10417.pdf
cuisine: Fusion
course: main course
